headline: CarParts.com Announces Evan Fischer® as Exclusive Brand on eBay
summary: CarParts.com, Inc. (NASDAQ: PRTS) today announced that its proprietary brand Evan Fischer® will now be offered exclusively on eBay as the only third-party marketplace where the brand is available.
